latestPosts.caption:
It is an honour to be considered by MasterPeace #CooLeaders to be its Global Ambassador.

I am excited for what lies ahead, especially  my interactions with fellow musicians and young CooLeaders across 70 countries.

Climate change is real and needs everyone to get involved and I am happy to start my journey towards building a Cooler and Greener Earth.

I remain grateful and will do my best for the cause. 

Thank you Sir @methaabu @culturemonks @masterpeace_global @tafmanagaland for all the support!!

latestPosts.caption:
Hey Guys!!
Global Earth Day is on April 22 and we pay our homage to Mother Nature. 
This year the theme is 'Our Power, Our Planet' .

 As the global ambassador of Masterpeace COOLeaders, I urge all of you to be aware and take steps to maintain the ecological balance, paving the way for better health and well being for all.

The change for a better tomorrow starts right now with small, thoughtful actions.
So let’s come together this Earth Day—not just to celebrate, but to ACT. 🌎 
#earthday2025 
#betterearthbetterfuture
‘Ka lawm e’ Mizoram 😊
